  <p class="sec-body" id="distNote" style="margin-bottom:18px">Sikkim's 4 districts showcase complete diversity from the cosmopolitan capital Gangtok to remote Kanyakumari, from the picturesque Mangan region to the serene Pelling area. Each district offers unique natural attractions and cultural experiences.</p>
